> 
>              total       used       free     shared    buffers     cached
> Mem:        517456     505332      12124     111016      97752     236884
> -/+ buffers/cache:     170696     346760
> Swap:       131048      23216     107832
> 
> Of course for me, I'm not about to waste 1gb of disk space for swap.
